data.description: Welcome to114 Morton Dr., where sophistication meets comfort! This charming residence features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, complemented by the allure of pristine hardwood floors throughout. The interior has undergone a meticulous remodel, elevating every corner with modern elegance. The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances that promise both functionality and style. Entertain effortlessly in the inviting living room and den, offering versatile spaces for relaxation and gatherings. This property embodies the perfect fusion of contemporary design and practical living, providing a truly exceptional living experience!
